Package hash_tables

Class SimpleHashSet

java.lang.Object
hash_tables.SimpleHashSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
SimpleSet
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClosedHashSet, OpenHashSet
public abstract class SimpleHashSet extends Object implements SimpleSet
A superclass for implementations of hash-sets implementing the hash_tables.SimpleSet interface.
